name: Romin Irani
bio: Romin Irani works as a Partner Engineer in the Google Cloud team, where his role is to make partners successful with GCP. He has a total of 25-years experience in the software industry across different roles and he has miles to go as he looks forward to the next 25 years.

name: Mayur Sojitra
bio: Mayur Sojitra is Full Stack Developer and Founder of Murait Technologies and have a expertise in multiple technologies. Having 6+ years of experience. Community Leader of Google Developers Group Surat, VueJS Surat and Laravel Surat.

name: Shashank Todwal
bio: Shashank Todwal has pursued B.E. (Hons.) Computer Science Engineering & M.Sc. (Hons.)Physics from BITS Pilani University. Before starting UMS Tech Labs, a Google Cloud Partner, Shashank worked for Google and interned under the guidance of renowned ProfessorRamakrishna Kakarala of Singapore, recipient of 26 US Patents.
